  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The intended use is benchmarking the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories for a Class II spinal fixation device under compression-bending loading per ASTM F1717. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) is below required level due to single test condition evaluated. Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance level.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
