      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA model inputs demonstrably matched to experimental specimen measurements",
      "rationale": "Screw and rod dimensions in FEA matched to micro-CT measurements of each physical specimen to within 0.05 mm. Locking torque applied in model matched to torque-wrench calibration records from each laboratory. Fixture geometry verified against test machine drawings."
